01", "language": "", "date_modified": "", "url": "http://www.ec.gc.ca/glaces-ice/default.asp?lang=En&n=D32C361E-1", "notes": "The CIS Digital Archive - Regional Charts collection consists of weekly Regional Ice Analysis Charts from 1968 to present in ArcGIS format. The paper charts from 1968 to 1998 were digitized in ArcGIS format and the dataset is updated in real-time. All charts for the Canadian Eastern and Western Arctic, the Hudson Bay, the East Coast of Canada, and the Great Lakes can be downloaded with the on-line charts interface.", "owner_org": "49E2ADF4-AD7A-43EB-85C8-6433D37ED62C", "keywords_fra": "\u00e9paisseur de la glace, Service canadien des glaces, ressources hydriques de l-arctique", "resource_type": "file"}
